00:32:55,029 --> 00:32:57,129
<b>- Since today? - No, it started a few days ago.</b>

440
00:33:01,339 --> 00:33:02,409
<b>What about our car?</b>

441
00:33:02,409 --> 00:33:05,279
<b>I'm checking every day if there's a tracker on it.</b>

442
00:33:14,018 --> 00:33:17,618
<b>(Special Exhibition on Leslie Cheung)</b>

443
00:33:25,429 --> 00:33:27,299
<b>Did you say you like movies?</b>

444
00:33:27,929 --> 00:33:29,399
<b>Yes, I like them very much.</b>

445
00:33:29,929 --> 00:33:32,469
<b>Do you want to watch a movie?</b>

446
00:33:33,069 --> 00:33:34,138
<b>Now?</b>

447
00:33:34,138 --> 00:33:36,909
<b>I know that I shouldn't be watching a movie right now.</b>

448
00:33:37,538 --> 00:33:38,909
<b>But it makes me think...</b>

449
00:33:39,609 --> 00:33:42,009
<b>if I'll have the right time to watch a movie.</b>

450
00:33:43,348 --> 00:33:44,918
<b>I'm totally in.</b>

451
00:34:15,149 --> 00:34:17,978
<b>(October 1994)</b>

452
00:34:50,179 --> 00:34:52,879
<b>My goodness. That was no fun at all. Let's just leave.</b>

453
00:34:53,618 --> 00:34:56,348
<b>My gosh, these movies from Hong Kong aren't like real movies.</b>

454
00:34:56,719 --> 00:34:59,219
<b>You know, the movie with Chow Yun Fat where he shoots guns?</b>

455
00:34:59,219 --> 00:35:00,888
<b>- Let's watch something like that. - What a waste of money.</b>

456
00:35:01,118 --> 00:35:02,228
<b>That was so boring.</b>

457
00:35:02,228 --> 00:35:04,529
<b>That movie from Hong Kong wasn't fun at all.</b>

458
00:35:04,529 --> 00:35:05,828
<b>Let's just go.</b>

459
00:35:06,859 --> 00:35:08,828
<b>- My gosh. - Darn it.</b>

460
00:35:17,469 --> 00:35:18,609
<b>Wait here.</b>

461
00:35:27,179 --> 00:35:28,348
<b>Your arms must hurt.</b>

462
00:35:29,918 --> 00:35:32,219
<b>How did you know that I would be here?</b>

