<b>You know that...</b>

695
00:56:12,998 --> 00:56:14,299
<b>I'm not going to take it.</b>

696
00:56:14,899 --> 00:56:18,668
<b>I do. I know that very well,</b>

697
00:56:19,498 --> 00:56:21,239
<b>but this was a promise made long ago,</b>

698
00:56:21,239 --> 00:56:23,438
<b>so I thought you would take it.</b>

699
00:56:24,909 --> 00:56:26,239
<b>And more than that, actually...</b>

700
00:56:29,578 --> 00:56:30,748
<b>It's because I missed you.</b>

701
00:56:53,799 --> 00:56:56,168
<b>My son is friends with Young Min. They are in the same class.</b>

702
00:56:56,509 --> 00:56:59,469
<b>Since you're here, I'll get going.</b>

703
00:56:59,469 --> 00:57:02,839
<b>(Han Jae Hyun)</b>

704
00:57:05,549 --> 00:57:07,949
<b>(Han Jae Hyun, Vice-President, Hyung Sung Group)</b>

705
00:57:07,949 --> 00:57:09,819
<b>("The Love Story Between the Owner's Daughter and the Employee")</b>

706
00:57:48,819 --> 00:57:50,688
<b>(When My Love Blooms)</b>

707
00:57:51,728 --> 00:57:52,958
<b>Do you regret it?</b>

708
00:57:54,029 --> 00:57:56,098
<b>I couldn't change anything, after all.</b>

709
00:57:57,399 --> 00:57:59,569
<b>I wasn't able to protect the most important thing.</b>

710
00:57:59,938 --> 00:58:02,339
<b>You should go your own way.</b>

711
00:58:02,969 --> 00:58:04,509
<b>And I'll go mine.</b>

712
00:58:05,038 --> 00:58:07,239
<b>He called it an affair. What I did.</b>

713
00:58:07,808 --> 00:58:11,179
<b>I'm going to make him take responsibility for what he did.</b>

714
00:58:11,909 --> 00:58:15,078
<b>I'm not here to blackmail you. I'm asking for your cooperation.</b>

715
00:58:16,989 --> 00:58:18,989
<b>Do what you want to do most...</b>

716
00:58:19,219 --> 00:58:21,688
<b>or avoid what you're most afraid of.</b>

717
00:58:24,529 --> 00:58:26,029
<b>This is just the beginning.</b>

718
00:58:26,929 --> 00:58:28,129
<b>It will be a long battle.</b>

